[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red0\green0\blue255;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Another \b hane and connection\b0  on the \b second line\b0 .
\par
\par It is getting more and more difficult, isn't it?
\par Let's count the value of Black 1 and 3. Don't forget about the continuation.
\par
\par After the hane and connection, both players have privilege to continue, so the value of this sequence is bigger.
\par
\par If there is \cf1\b no privilege\cf0\b0  to continue, the hane and connection on the second line is worth \cf1\b 6 points\cf0\b0 , but if there is continuation, the value is increasing.
\par
\par
\par
\par }
